{"tid":1162211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[收皮啦侵侵]拜登第一場大型造勢活動　狠批特朗普「分化大王」","createTime":"2019-05-19T17:15:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T03:48:07.000Z","uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4679e98af48f431ced08a818a14cbb2fc6dc8703","tid":1162211,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:15:44.000Z","msg":"美國前副總統拜登（Joe Biden）宣布參選2020美國總統選舉後，上周六（18日）在其第一場大型造勢活動中呼籲全國團結。<br />\n<br />\n他也直接在演說中指出：「我們總統是分化大王（divider-in-chief）。」看來他已將眼光放在2020年黨內初選之後，進入頻密及直接攻擊現任總統特朗普（Donald Trump）的狀態。<br />\n<br />\n賓夕法尼亞州是拜登的出生地，也是他競選總部所在地。他的演說以團結及共識為中心，用以回應外界有聲音指出，他想要做到跨越黨派界線的希望是天真的，而其認為共和黨人會在特朗普離去後「頓悟」的想法也是不會變真的。<br />\n<br />\n他對現場數千群眾說：「我們已觀察他3年。讓我們看看他在做什麼。（對全美）灌輸恐懼。我不是在說笑，他是灌輸恐懼、為分化的播種、煽動種族分化。」他說特朗普政府是「對這個國家的威脅、對我們民主的威脅。」<br />\n<br />\n他說：「如果美國民眾想要一個令我們更分化的總統、以緊握的拳頭以及封閉的心、去妖魔化對手以及吐出仇恨&mdash;&mdash;他們不需要我。他們已經有一個做到這事的總統了。我參選是為向我們的國家&mdash;&mdash;民主黨人、共和黨人及獨立人士&mdash;&mdash;提供一條不同的路。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登這番話顯示他與特朗普的互相批評升級。這也是宣布參加2020年大選的眾多民主黨候選人當中，最進取地、直接地批評特朗普分化及種族主義言論的一人。<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/330751/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E9%80%A0%E5%8B%A2%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F330751%2F%25E6%258B%259C%25E7%2599%25BB%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259E%258B%25E9%2580%25A0%25E5%258B%25A2%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E5%258B%2595-%25E7%258B%25A0%25E6%2589%25B9%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE-%25E5%2588%2586%25E5%258C%2596%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%258E%258B&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ14T2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=dae84bc6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/330751/%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%A0%B4%E5%A4%A7%E5%9E%8B%E9%80%A0%E5%8B%A2%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95-%E7%8B%A0%E6%89%B9%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE-%E5%88%86%E5%8C%96%E5%A4%A7%E7%8E%8B</a>"},{"pid":"55a28045097da07fa6c0521574f5d0b4bff39e7b","tid":1162211,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:34:06.000Z","msg":"拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拜登<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed89f4bb3154afd8b1bfb4c8f54110fd33842ea9","tid":1162211,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"佢選閪到咩"},{"pid":"59738b1865696a263a461ef38359974bda959c6b","tid":1162211,"uid":36551,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:42:19.000Z","msg":"屎為狗幾時去加拿大救慢慢周呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3734d41f35190967b78a088303d9eb02cc1de8","tid":1162211,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"實有cp流出"},{"pid":"4011061105c4eb5270f7907adc35ba6c8f9a2c33","tid":1162211,"uid":125193,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"我參選是為向我們的國家&mdash;&mdash;民主黨人、共和黨人及獨立人士&mdash;&mdash;提供一條不同的路。」<br />\n<br />\n暗示奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbut Trump 只要講拜登有親中利益關係+佢個仔收左中共錢 佢就<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55aff4a87f2305b7257b9c94a8aa5b4610cc3d7f","tid":1162211,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T17:50:05.000Z","msg":"呢條友選到<br />\n<br />\n支共 會贏得呢場戰爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9955f5b53